FBIS3-23044 "jptot008__l94136" JPRS-TOT-94-008-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 1 March 1994 WEST EUROPE TURKEY Two People Killed in Attack on Mardin Minibus TA1702174794 Ankara ANATOLIA in English 1620 GMT 17 Feb 94 TA1702174794 Ankara ANATOLIA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] Diyarbakir, Feb 17 (AA) -- Two people, one of them a village headman, were killed in attack in Midyat township in southeastern Mardin Province on Wednesday, it was reported on Thursday. AA was told that the incident happened when unidentified assailants opened gunfire on a village minibus. [passage omitted]
